Package: pdactrace
Type: Package
Title: Queryable Stage-Aware PDAC Tissue-to-Serum Biomarker Reference Atlas
Version: 0.99.2
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Jibeom", family = "Ko",
           email = "rhwlqja1779@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-8630-1973")))
Description: pdactrace exposes a stage-aware pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma
    (PDAC) tissue-to-serum biomarker reference atlas across bulk RNA-seq,
    tissue proteomics, single-cell origin, and serum proteomics. The current
    release supports deterministic lookup, transparent GraphAudit evidence
    aggregation, external-anchor enrichment evaluation, and Monte Carlo
    uncertainty propagation. The package does not train a supervised biomarker
    predictor because validated non-circular PDAC early-detection ground truth
    is not available.
